{"tid":30881,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"第一屆lihk壇花壇草選舉","createTime":"2016-12-09T10:58:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T12:07:22.000Z","uid":19305,"like":880,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"57fb5b5fe0cdf55e77b147e125de7aac667f030e","tid":30881,"uid":19305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:58:33.000Z","msg":"請自貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味係咪要搞到咁撚樣先開心啊<br />\n仆你個街成群人係到打撚哂5p字<br />\n開撚埋哂d濕鳩交配po<br />\n唔好話上個壇識朋友有乜撚野問題<br />\n你班撚屌自問係識朋友咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個撚個係到搵西屌<br />\n屌那星高登08年之前一直都好撚抗拒5p文化<br />\n唔知幾撚時開始高登都變撚埋5p<br />\n又開撚埋d濕鳩群 你老咪臭閪有乜撚野唔可以係到講<br />\n諗住過撚到黎會冇撚哂班5p柒頭 屌你老尾仲多撚過之前高登 仲要惡撚過高登<br />\nLihk第一日開果時d po係幾撚咁高質 有返以前高登味道 點知唔夠兩個星期比班柒頭搞到成個lihk污煙瘴氣 同5p有乜撚野分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一日再唔撚改善 呢到只會變第二個高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32fd5c9cd86b2b1ee7ebb7ee630e316e27f7de54","tid":30881,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"本身諗住入黎屌柒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa948058d19476a45829123976a9c76754f7a85","tid":30881,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:00:01.000Z","msg":"仆街未睇內文比左負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f1ae5e47a17af6916c4cd0270a4a5e42ec3fac","tid":30881,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:00:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仆街未睇內文比左負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\